snippet.title: Cluck and Conquer Alpha Trailer
snippet.description: Cluck and Conquer is a roguelite, micro-focused RTS where you command an army of battle-ready chickens! Expand, unlock and upgrade your flock into a feathery force of destruction. Try the demo: https://soy-boy-games.itch.io/cluckandconquer
